<Content>Classic Classic hotel inaugurated by Porfirio Diaz in 1904. Completely refurbished and air conditioned in 1956. Excellent location right on Reforma, near Juarez and just a few blocks from the Metro on Balderas. Elegant high ceilings, excellent service and a good restaurant; bathrooms with showers over tubs. Reasonable prices and seasonal special offers. 
